CatDescriptText: Sign in background reads "We regret this announcement.  We are forced to close after 13 years due to redevelopment,  We will be at our other tavern 3237 Penn Ave. until we find a suitable location to better serve you in East Liberty,  We wish to thank all out faithful friends & customers for their [many?] years of support.  And we will make every effort to re-locate to serve you better in East Liberty.  Closing date July 30."
TitMainTitle: Interior of bar or restaurant with booths, checkered tile floor, wooden paneling, and sign reading "We regret this announcement..." possibly Williams - Luck Tavern
